title: Murders In The Rue Morgue
info:
MURDERS IN THE RUE MORGUE



Written by Iron Maiden
Covered by Malekith for BEST OF THE FANS III musicdisk.

Well, i don't have much to say here... A fast heavy tune with a very quiet
intro, a good old Maiden song with Di'Anno. I didn't use any "vocal"
sample because I think the guitar melodies are enough (the vocal parts are
nearly the same).

Thanx to Betrayer and Cadaver for samples.
Hails to Dragon, Hakan and everyone I have forgotten, I don't write all
the names but you know who you are ! UP THE IRONS !

Playing time : 4'07. Hope you like this !
